data.description: Available now -live in the heart of Del Ray! Light-filled cozy 1 Bedroom 1 Bath top/2nd floor corner unit w/two sides of windows, open floor plan & generous closet storage. Additional storage cage in basement & 1 off-street reserved parking pass. Rent Incl: free laundry in basement, bicycle storage, water & sewer, trash, central community water heater, snow removal. Suggested income to qualify should be a minimum of 45 times the monthly rent amount. Pets considered case by case.
